And happiness.

00:21.551 --> 00:24.550
Can Rodrigo's eyes come out to play?

00:24.551 --> 00:26.550
No. No, they'll stay in.

00:26.551 --> 00:28.550
Ah. Okay, the glasses stay on.

00:28.551 --> 00:30.751
Uh, Hendrik, get the maestro a baton.

00:31.551 --> 00:33.550
Thank you.

00:33.551 --> 00:35.550
Happiness. That... That
uh... That looks great.

00:35.551 --> 00:37.550
You ever held one of those before?

00:37.551 --> 00:40.550
Ha ha ha ha ha ha!

00:40.551 --> 00:42.751
And, maestro, conduct!

00:43.551 --> 00:46.550
With passion.

00:46.551 --> 00:47.550
You have ten shots.

00:47.551 --> 00:49.751
Happiness.

00:51.551 --> 00:52.550
That was eight.

00:52.551 --> 00:53.550
You only have two left.

00:53.551 --> 00:55.550
W-What?

00:55.551 --> 00:56.550
You have two left.

00:56.551 --> 00:57.550
We just started.

00:57.551 --> 00:59.751
You want passion?

01:03.551 --> 01:04.751
[shutter clicks]

01:08.551 --> 01:11.751
This is the best photograph
I've ever taken.

